The paper deals with lossless compression of inverted indices, which are commonly used in information retrieval (IR) systems such as web search and online advertising. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves matrix factorization, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and data mining (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper deals with data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.AI) for query evaluation.
